metadata.name: "Lift Off" Rare Scented Candle
metadata.description:
Launching you up and through multiple worlds, this fresh-to-death scented candle will energise any room you burn it. Flavours including refreshing clary sage and razor-sharp fir needle are guaranteed to emit a cleansing but powerful throw. 

A unique blend of fragrance oils inspired by science fantasy, mixed with vegan mica powder, you'll see and smell a firework-like display, as seen on @planet_ry

Shipping:
Included in price
Please fill out google form (link to form comes with purchase) with your ETH & physical address.
